{"tid":141554,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝返學同件有幾舊腹肌既mk隻揪","createTime":"2017-03-03T04:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T07:28:59.000Z","uid":153,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f611ff43fd1e3a390cdfb1d0e8c83561462baa74","tid":141554,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學 <br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪 <br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打 <br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉 <br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型 <br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿 <br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」 <br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」 <br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲 <br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量 <br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過 <br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間 <br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇 <br />\n佢就除左件校服 <br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋 <br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"0b8522d6fbd71865fbbe346f0e4c7f0489c232e4","tid":141554,"uid":68867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43e86ea500eaba971e10dd18addc2597676f677","tid":141554,"uid":33958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414be1df64dcf44e70a36d9ea4f55510c5ad0023","tid":141554,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=